## 1. Tech Stack (Frontend)

| Layer | Technology | Rationale |
|:---|:---|:---|
| **Framework** | Next.js 14 (App Router) | SSR, RSC, Middleware auth guard, file-based routing |
| **Styling** | Vanilla CSS + CSS Variables | Kontrol penuh atas design system, tanpa overhead framework CSS |
| **Charts** | Lightweight Charts (TradingView) + Recharts | Equity curve = Lightweight Charts; Bar/Donut = Recharts |
| **Auth** | NextAuth.js v5 (Auth.js) | Discord OAuth2 SSO, JWT sessions, middleware protection |
| **Icons** | Lucide React | Konsisten, ringan, tree-shakeable |
| **Fonts** | JetBrains Mono + Inter | Monospace untuk angka/data, Sans untuk body text |
| **State** | React Context + Server Components | Minimal client state; data-fetch di server |
| **DB ORM** | Prisma | Type-safe, mendukung MongoDB |

