## 4. Page Specifications

### 4.1 Landing Page (`/`)

**Purpose:** Akuisisi & konversi — memastikan hanya member Hunter Trades yang masuk.

**Layout:** Full-page, no sidebar. Centered content.

**Sections:**

1. **Hero Section**
   - Tagline: `"YOUR EDGE. TRACKED."` (H1, `--text-hero`, gold accent pada "EDGE")
   - Subline: `"Jurnal trading eksklusif untuk member Hunter Trades"` (muted)
   - CTA Button: `"Login with Discord"` (bg: `--accent-purple`, icon Discord, rounded-full)
   - Background: Subtle animated grid/dot pattern dengan parallax

2. **Feature Triptych** (3 kartu glassmorphism horizontal)
   - 🛡 **Risk Engine** — "Prop-firm style drawdown tracking"
   - 📖 **Playbook System** — "Disiplinkan trading dengan metodologi"
   - 📊 **Deep Analytics** — "Breakdown performa per pair & strategi"

3. **Social Proof Footer**
   - "Powered by Hunter Trades Community"
   - Statistik: member count, total trades logged (dynamic, fetched from DB)

**Animations:**
- Hero text: staggered fade-up (0ms, 200ms, 400ms)
- Feature cards: fade-up on scroll intersection
- Grid background: subtle floating animation

