### 4.5 Trade Logger (`/log-trade`)

**Purpose:** Input entri trade yang cepat, efisien, dan disiplin (wajib link ke playbook).

**Layout:** 2-column: Main form (left, 60%) + Live Risk Preview (right, 40%)

**Form Fields (grouped):**

#### Group 1 — Meta
| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|:---|:---|:---|:---|
| Tanggal & Waktu | DateTime picker | ✅ | Default: sekarang |
| Pair / Asset | Searchable dropdown | ✅ | Pre-populated: XAUUSD, EURUSD, GBPUSD, USDJPY, dll |
| Direction | Toggle button | ✅ | `LONG` (green) / `SHORT` (red) |
| Playbook | Dropdown | ✅ | **Hanya menampilkan playbook yang sudah dibuat user** |

#### Group 2 — Financials
| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|:---|:---|:---|:---|
| Entry Price | Number input | ✅ | Monospace styling |
| Stop Loss | Number input | ✅ | Auto-calculates risk |
| Take Profit | Number input | ❌ | Optional (trailing exit, etc) |
| Lot Size | Number input | ✅ | Position sizing |
| Actual PnL | Number input | ✅ | Green/red text based on value |

#### Group 3 — Metrics (Auto-calculated where possible)
| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|:---|:---|:---|:---|
| R-Multiple | Auto / Manual | ✅ | Auto = PnL / Risk. Editable override. |
| Result | Toggle 3-way | ✅ | `WIN` / `LOSS` / `BREAK-EVEN` |

#### Group 4 — Psychology & Notes
| Field | Type | Required | Notes |
|:---|:---|:---|:---|
| Emotional State | 5-point emoji scale | ❌ | 😡 Tilted → 😐 Neutral → 😌 Confident |
| Notes / Journaling | Textarea | ❌ | Markdown support |
| Chart Link | URL input | ❌ | TradingView deeplink |

#### Live Risk Preview Sidebar
Sidebar yang meng-update secara real-time seiring user mengisi form:
- **"Dampak Trade Ini"**
- Position Size: X lots
- Risk Amount: $Y (berdasarkan Entry - SL × lot)
- Risk as % of Equity: Z%
- **Drawdown Impact Preview:**
  - "Jika trade ini LOSS, drawdown harian Anda menjadi: **X% → Y%**"
  - Visual bar showing before/after
  - ⚠️ Warning jika akan melampaui batas

#### Submit Flow:
1. Validasi semua required fields
2. Jika risk melebihi daily limit → Confirmation modal: "Trade ini akan membuat Anda **melampaui batas drawdown harian**. Tetap lanjutkan?"
3. Submit → Success toast → Redirect ke Dashboard

