### 4.6 Playbook Manager (`/playbook`)

**Purpose:** Definisikan dan kelola strategi trading (playbook).

**Layout:** Grid view (default) / List view (toggle). Card-based.

**Playbook Card:**
```
┌──────────────────────────────┐
│  📖 London Breakout          │
│  ─────────────────────────   │
│  Pairs: GBPUSD, EURUSD      │
│  Session: London             │
│  Win Rate: 68% (34/50)       │
│  Avg R: 1.8R                 │
│                              │
│  [Edit]  [View Rules]        │
└──────────────────────────────┘
```

**Create / Edit Playbook Modal/Page:**
- **Name:** Text input (e.g. "SMC Liquidity Sweep")
- **Description:** Textarea
- **Applicable Pairs:** Multi-select Tags
- **Session:** Dropdown (London / NY / Asian / All)
- **Rules / Checklist:** Repeatable text fields
  - e.g. "Tunggu Break of Structure (BOS) pada M15"
  - e.g. "Entry hanya jika ada imbalance / FVG"
  - e.g. "Minimum RR 1:2"
- **Tags:** Freeform tags for categorization

**Playbook Detail View (`/playbook/[id]`):**
- Full rules checklist
- Historical stats: Win rate, total trades, avg R, profit factor
- Recent trades using this playbook (linked from trade log)
- Mini equity curve for trades under this playbook

