## 7. Responsive Design Strategy

### Breakpoints

```css
/* Mobile First */
@media (min-width: 640px)  { /* sm — Small tablet */ }
@media (min-width: 768px)  { /* md — Tablet */ }
@media (min-width: 1024px) { /* lg — Small desktop */ }
@media (min-width: 1280px) { /* xl — Desktop (primary) */ }
@media (min-width: 1536px) { /* 2xl — Large monitor */ }
```

### Layout Adaptations

| Page | Desktop (≥1280) | Tablet (768-1279) | Mobile (<768) |
|:---|:---|:---|:---|
| **Dashboard** | 3-col bento grid | 2-col grid | 1-col stack |
| **Log Trade** | Form + sidebar | Form full-width, sidebar below | Single column |
| **Playbook** | 3-col card grid | 2-col grid | 1-col stack |
| **Analytics** | Charts + tables side-by-side | Charts stacked | Charts stacked, horizontal scroll table |

### Mobile-Specific UX
- **Bottom Action Bar:** Floating button "＋ Log Trade" selalu terlihat di mobile
- **Swipe gestures:** Swipe trade row → quick actions (edit / delete)
- **Collapsible sections:** Accordion-style for analytics breakdowns

